Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(286,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  鹰志  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚远一点  你这狐狸精
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(167,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰志是哥哥  得护着小鸠一点才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么跟那女人鬼混啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(253,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰志很喜欢小鸠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要永远和睦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少给我扯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波她没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波什么都没有做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这么欺负波波啊

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TITLE-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:58.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的翅膀…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一直是个心灵很脆弱的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法跟爸爸住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(422,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把爸爸的影子重叠在了鹰志身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛跟那女人缠在一块啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无法容忍同一屋檐下的义弟的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是小鸠  与鹰志君亲密相处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接着走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  别这么下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在失去了格雷塔加尔德的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次与存在在我身体里的两人相遇并对话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了我的存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该是代替蜗居于地狱的羽田鹰志而诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都温柔  不知疼痛的无敌英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(394,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我  羽田鹰志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  我的存在并不完全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦无法承受心灵上的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就马上会逃匿到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候所沉迷的游戏  WING QUEST的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷塔加尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了支撑的这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁鹫介和成田隼人也诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(412,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还跟我说  为了小鸠  想把鹰志找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  我提出得面对过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始两个人都很反对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最终还是接受了这个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦你再逛一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒也没什么所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是M吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤先生一定会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心爱的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的车  开起来有点不顺手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气  不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  凤先生也有妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这车胎还真滑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点儿也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个教会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负我们的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我哭泣  令我发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至差点失去意识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我很希望有谁能向我伸出援手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却总是有某样重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去保护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Cab Killer Movie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Cab killer Movie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不下去就别忍了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不废话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我亲手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会再原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会得到宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不能存在于这世上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我选择了逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再回忆起这样的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不被过去责难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是地狱之刑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我应有的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱什么的我真的受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想跟大家一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以忘记所有不愉快的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续活在地狱里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说梦电视也看得超过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JO俺X-TV
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所看到的是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽田君最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿世界永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿世界永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿世界永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿世界永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们小时候  这里曾经有过很照顾我们的牧师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话是那位牧师教我们的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说「愿主赐你一颗宽恕万物的心」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了不可饶恕的地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧师先生吩咐我当你想起了一切的时候交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}（母子自杀未遂）\N（母亲服毒自杀）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服毒自杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…我一手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的伤痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得哥哥的母亲由始至终都不打算活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我出了手这个事实还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  哥哥可是守护了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠才茁壮成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  都成大鸠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿世界永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你一直都有着一颗宽恕万物的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也宽恕自己一回啊
