Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了  一块儿上学去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥
